  "detailed_description": "<strong>Lock’n Load into a world of pixels!</strong><br><br>2 Many Pixels is an endless & fast-paced 2D minimal shooter. Blast enemies & unlock upgrades to help you survive for as long as possible!<br><br>I bet you think you're a pro gamer, maybe even a god gamer and have been playing games all your life with thousands of hours played... Well, it's time to put those hours to use and show off your wicked-sick gaming skills to all your friends!<br><br>Prove you're not a complete noob and that years of being addicted to playing video games has been worth it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Blast endless waves of enemies.<br></li><li> Survive for as long as you can.<br></li><li> Earn tokens from killing enemies.<br></li><li> Equip permanent upgrades.<br></li><li> Achievements!<br></li><li> Trash Talker - to remind you how noob you are.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230040/extras/f50291fa5f537fef90d294bee2152299.avif?t=1698078305\" width=420 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230040/extras/0898f35a5b10b2df73c1a2b230dc4ebd.avif?t=1698078305\" width=420 height=196 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230040/extras/a0ae72235bddd9a823b870c1eb4105aa.avif?t=1698078305\" width=420 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230040/extras/74a9bb700eff402228eceaf7cc29aebb.avif?t=1698078305\" width=420 height=146 /></span>",
